CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1773083490
OL,3,CBomb victim alleges Gerry Adams
OL,4,C'directly responsible' for IRA attack
OL,6,FGerry Adams was "directly responsible
OL,7,Ffor and complicit" in the decisions
OL,8,Fmade by the Provisional IRA to
OL,9,Fdetonate bombs in Manchester and
OL,10,FLondon, the High Court has heard.
OL,12,FBarry Laycock, a victim of the 1996
OL,13,FArndale shopping centre bombing in
OL,14,FManchester, John Clark, a victim of
OL,15,Fthe 1973 Old Bailey bombing in London
OL,16,Fand Jonathan Ganesh, a 1996 London
OL,17,FDocklands bombing victim allege that
OL,18,FMr Adams was a leading member of the
OL,19,FProvisional IRA on those dates,
OL,20,Fincluding of its Army Council.
OL,26,@nD@QOUoD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1773083490
OL,3,CBomb victim alleges Gerry Adams
OL,4,C'directly responsible' for IRA attack
OL,6,FThe three men are bringing legal
OL,7,Faction against the former Sinn Fein
OL,8,Fpresident and are seeking #1 in
OL,9,Fdamages.
OL,11,FMr Adams denies that he had any role
OL,12,Fin the Provisional IRA and is opposing
OL,13,Fthe claim.
OL,15,FOn Monday he arrived at the Royal
OL,16,FCourts of Justice wearing what
OL,17,Fappeared to be a bullet-proof vest,
OL,18,Fand was driven into the car park.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1773083490
OL,3,CBomb victim alleges Gerry Adams
OL,4,C'directly responsible' for IRA attack
OL,6,FThe court in London heard that the
OL,7,Fthree men want to show how Mr Adams
OL,8,Fwas involved in the Provisional IRA
OL,9,F"in the course of that conflict and to
OL,10,Fshow on the balance of probabilities
OL,11,Fthat he was as involved as the people
OL,12,Fwho planted and detonated those bombs".
OL,14,FOpening her case on Monday, Anne Studd
OL,15,FKC, representing the men, also said Mr
OL,16,FAdams was "directly responsible for
OL,17,Fand complicit in those decisions made
OL,18,Fby that organisation to detonate bombs
OL,19,Fon the British mainland in 1973 and
OL,20,F1996".
OL,26,@qD@AOUtD@fO]xD@KOU|D@EO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1773083490
OL,3,CBomb victim alleges Gerry Adams
OL,4,C'directly responsible' for IRA attack
OL,6,FIn written submissions, Ms Studd said:
OL,7,F"The defendant carefully draws a
OL,8,Fdistinction between being a member of
OL,9,F'the Army' and being a member of Sinn
OL,10,FFein.
OL,12,F"In reality, the evidence will
OL,13,Fdemonstrate that this was not the
OL,14,Fclear either/or choice as the
OL,15,Fdefendant would have you believe.
OL,17,F"For many individuals, we say,
OL,18,Fincluding Mr Adams, that was a
OL,19,Fdistinction without a difference."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU{D@bO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1773083490
OL,3,CBomb victim alleges Gerry Adams
OL,4,C'directly responsible' for IRA attack
OL,6,FMs Studd told the court that a
OL,7,F"jigsaw" of evidence from those who
OL,8,Fknew Mr Adams and those who knew of
OL,9,Fhim will prove the case against him.
OL,11,FShe added: "The claimants' case is
OL,12,Fthat none of these bombings in the
OL,13,FUnited Kingdom mainland took place
OL,14,Fwithout the knowledge and agreement of
OL,15,Fthe defendant in his role in the
OL,16,FProvisional IRA and latterly as a
OL,17,Fmember of the seven-man Army Council."
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@HO]sD@LOUyD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1773083490
OL,3,CBomb victim alleges Gerry Adams
OL,4,C'directly responsible' for IRA attack
OL,6,FShe concluded: "There is no doubt that
OL,7,Fthe defendant contributed to the peace
OL,8,Fin Northern Ireland, but the claimants
OL,9,Fsay that on the evidence he also
OL,10,Fcontributed to the war."
OL,12,FLawyers for Mr Adams, who denies the
OL,13,Fclaims, said Mr Adams "played an
OL,14,Finstrumental role in the peace process
OL,15,Fwhich culminated in the signing of the
OL,16,FGood Friday Agreement in April 1998,
OL,17,Fwhich brought an end to the decades-
OL,18,Flong conflict".
OL,26,@nD@POUrD@XO]uD@WOUzD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1773083490
OL,3,CBomb victim alleges Gerry Adams
OL,4,C'directly responsible' for IRA attack
OL,6,FIn written submissions, Edward Craven
OL,7,FKC, representing Mr Adams, said: "The
OL,8,Fdefendant's alleged factual and legal
OL,9,Fresponsibility for the claimants'
OL,10,Finjuries is strongly contested, as is
OL,11,Fthe claimants' ability to bring these
OL,12,Fclaims against the defendant several
OL,13,Fdecades after the expiry of the
OL,14,Fapplicable limitation period."
OL,16,FHe added that there is "no legal or
OL,17,Fpractical reason why these claims
OL,18,Fcould not have been issued long before
OL,19,F2022".
OL,26,@oD@bOUvD@^O]xD@XOU{D@EO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1773083490
OL,3,CBomb victim alleges Gerry Adams
OL,4,C'directly responsible' for IRA attack
OL,6,FMr Craven continued: "Even if the
OL,7,Fclaim were not bound to fail on
OL,8,Flimitation grounds, the claim must
OL,9,Finevitably fail on the merits.
OL,11,F"The defendant strenuously denies any
OL,12,Finvolvement in the bombings."
OL,14,FHe also said: "The defendant has never
OL,15,Fbeen arrested on suspicion of, still
OL,16,Fless charged or convicted of, any
OL,17,Foffence in connection with any of the
OL,18,Fbombings.
OL,26,@nD@VOUsD@AOUtD@]O]vD@OOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1773083490
OL,3,CBomb victim alleges Gerry Adams
OL,4,C'directly responsible' for IRA attack
OL,6,F"Had law enforcement authorities been
OL,7,Fin possession of information which
OL,8,Fcreated a reasonable suspicion that
OL,9,Fthe defendant may have been involved
OL,10,Fin those bombings, he would have been
OL,11,Farrested and questioned."
OL,13,FThe trial before Mr Justice Swift is
OL,14,Fexpected to end next week.
OL,16,FTwo IRA members planted the biggest
OL,17,Fbomb on the UK mainland since World
OL,18,FWar Two targeting shoppers at the
OL,19,FManchester Arndale shopping centre on
OL,20,Fa Saturday on 15 June 1996.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1773083490
OL,3,CBomb victim alleges Gerry Adams
OL,4,C'directly responsible' for IRA attack
OL,6,FIt caused extensive damage and an
OL,7,Fevacuation, but no-one was killed. 200
OL,8,Fpeople were injured and some were left
OL,9,Ftraumatised by the attack.
OL,11,FJust before 10:00am, Gary Hall, a
OL,12,Fsecurity guard at ITV's Granada
OL,13,Fstudios received a phone call from a
OL,14,Fman with a "very calm" Irish voice.
OL,15,FThe man said he had planted a bomb
OL,16,Fthat would explode an hour later.
OL,18,FShortly afterwards, police began
OL,19,Fevacuating about 80,000 people from
OL,20,Fthe city centre, while attempts were
OL,21,Fmade to find the bomb.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1773083490
OL,3,CBomb victim alleges Gerry Adams
OL,4,C'directly responsible' for IRA attack
OL,6,FAmid the panic, a police officer
OL,7,Fspotted the white lorry and noticed
OL,8,Fwires running from the dashboard.
OL,10,FBomb disposal officers attempted to
OL,11,Fdefuse the explosive with a remote-
OL,12,Fcontrolled robot.
OL,14,FThe attempt failed and at 11:17am the
OL,15,F3,300lb device exploded. Smoke
OL,16,Fmushroomed high above the city while
OL,17,Fbuildings shook and glass shattered,
OL,18,Fraining debris on people outside the
OL,19,Fcordoned area.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
